{"tid":2332894,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"福布斯2020球壇收入榜：C.朗拿度力壓美斯 中超1人上榜","createTime":"2020-12-20T03:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:03:49.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7b6f0438a38dac25bc861eaf153113e891b502","tid":2332894,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"根據福布斯公佈的榜單，2020年球壇收入最高的球員是C.朗拿度，美斯排在第二。<br />\n<br />\n  福布斯的榜單將工資、贊助收入等全部計算在內，C.朗拿度以8580萬英鎊排在第一，美斯以8340萬英鎊位列第二。在榜單中，中超巴西球星奧斯卡進入了前十名。<br />\n<br />\n  2020年收入最高的十名球員（福布斯榜單）<br />\n<br />\n  1、C.朗拿度、祖雲達斯、8580萬英鎊<br />\n<br />\n  2、美斯、巴塞隆拿、8340萬<br />\n<br />\n  3、尼馬、巴黎聖日耳門、7660萬<br />\n<br />\n  4、沙拿、利物浦、2820萬<br />\n<br />\n  5、麥巴比、巴黎聖日耳門、2710萬<br />\n<br />\n  6、恩尼斯達、神戶勝利船、2370萬<br />\n<br />\n  7、奧斯爾、阿仙奴、2300萬<br />\n<br />\n  8、普巴、曼聯、2280萬<br />\n<br />\n  9、奧斯卡、上海上港、2200萬<br />\n<br />\n  10、基沙文、巴塞隆拿、2140萬"},{"pid":"3a7cc8e72e96dacdf9b544170e91e1e180570aa9","tid":2332894,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"神戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35320c3c9a5c8b32148e802470980f7659064ae2","tid":2332894,"uid":14454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"奧燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐喺度收錢"},{"pid":"4985b64814ad826add46d2ac34d92a286770476a","tid":2332894,"uid":136416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35320c3c9a5c8b32148e802470980f7659064ae2","tid":2332894,"uid":14454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"奧燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐喺度收錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"除返開<br />\n勞動時數薪金比<br />\n奧燒一定第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26fe5d60ce8160722559f345d25d734d9f2f7a2","tid":2332894,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislik